================================================================================
SECTION A: MANDALORIAN SOVEREIGNTY LICENSE v1.0 (Open Source)
================================================================================

Permission is hereby granted, free of charge, to any person obtaining a copy
of this software and associated documentation files (the "Software"), to deal
in the Software without restriction, including without limitation the rights
to use, copy, modify, merge, publish, distribute, sublicense, and/or sell
copies of the Software, subject to the following SOVEREIGNTY CONDITIONS:

1. NO BACKDOORS
   You may NOT introduce any mechanism allowing access to user data, system
   functions, or cryptographic keys without explicit, real-time, informed
   consent from the user. This includes law enforcement access, vendor
   overrides, remote access without authorization, key escrow, or hidden
   administrative accounts.

2. SHIELD LEDGER IMMUTABILITY
   You MUST preserve the integrity and immutability of the Shield Ledger.
   Any modification allowing deletion or suppression of security audit
   events voids your license.

3. REPRODUCIBLE BUILDS
   You MUST provide complete build instructions yielding bit-for-bit
   identical binaries when built by independent parties.

4. TRANSPARENCY
   You MUST clearly document hardware dependencies, security limitations,
   and simulation-only code.

5. USER SOVEREIGNTY
   The user retains absolute authority over their device. Any mechanism
   subverting user control voids your license.

6. COPYLEFT REQUIREMENT
   If you distribute modified versions or use this Software in a service,
   you MUST release your modifications under this same license.

THE SOFTWARE IS PROVIDED "AS IS", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND.

================================================================================
SECTION B: COMMERCIAL LICENSE (Enterprise/Government)
================================================================================

For organizations requiring:
- Proprietary use without copyleft obligations
- Commercial support and SLAs
- Custom feature development
- White-label licensing
- Government/defense sovereign deployments

Contact: info@socialfeed.co.za
Subject: "Mandalorian Commercial License Inquiry"

Pricing Tiers:
- Enterprise: $50,000 - $500,000/year per organization
- Government/Defense: Custom pricing ($1M+)
- Hardware OEM: Per-device licensing

Commercial licenses include:
- Dedicated support channel
- Priority security updates
- Custom HSM integration
- Compliance documentation
- Training and onboarding

================================================================================
WHICH LICENSE SHOULD I CHOOSE?
================================================================================

Choose MANDALORIAN SOVEREIGNTY LICENSE if:
✓ You are an individual user or researcher
✓ You are building open-source projects
✓ You believe in software freedom and transparency
✓ You will share your improvements with the community

Choose COMMERCIAL LICENSE if:
✓ You are a corporation building proprietary products
✓ You need legal indemnification
✓ You require professional support
✓ You cannot comply with copyleft requirements
✓ You are a government/defense organization

